(228, 1, '2019-12-05 10:21:23', '2019-12-05 10:21:23', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MPTeq was established in 2016 to provide specialised processing equipment to the minerals processing industry.&nbsp; The initial focus was on thickeners but our product offering has since expanded to include jigs, filters, larcodems, mixing and agitation systems, as well as attrition scrubbers, linear screens and log washers through partnerships and exclusive distribution rights.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All our thickeners and equipment designs are certified and signed off by a registered professional engineer as are our design drawings.&nbsp; We specify and install only proven mechanical, electrical and instrumentation borne out by the fact that our personnel have never had a single failure despite having thickeners installed globally.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Our Company', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-company', '', '', '2019-12-05 10:21:23', '2019-12-05 10:21:23', '', 0, 'https://cmfreelancing.co.za/client_sites/MPTeq/?page_id=228', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(229, 1, '2019-12-05 10:21:49', '2019-12-05 10:21:49', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MPTeq&nbsp;offers a complete line of high-rate, traction, ultra-high density or paste thickeners based on the latest proven designs.&nbsp; Jigs, filters, larcodems, mixing and agitation systems, as well as attrition scrubbers, linear screens and log washers all form part of our product lines.&nbsp; Our team brings extensive experience to meet your process needs having designed, manufactured, commissioned and operated these units for many years. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We understand minerals processing and our equipment is engineered and manufactured to the highest standard.&nbsp; It offers the precision and durability required to keep your process going, being custom designed for each project.&nbsp; When selecting the right equipment for you, we will determine the most cost-effective mechanism for your application without compromising availability or production. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MPTeq’s engineers can help you with the design of your total flowsheet, ensuring that all your equipment will work together for ease of operation and optimal performance.&nbsp; Sizing and specifying process equipment, specifically a thickener can be difficult, and MPTeq’s trained personnel can provide you with the available alternatives and help you select the right equipment for your process application.&nbsp; Correct sizing of your equipment will assure a margin of safety for process upsets and allow greatest operational flexibility.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Our Products', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-products', '', '', '2019-12-05 10:21:49', '2019-12-05 10:21:49', '', 0, 'https://cmfreelancing.co.za/client_sites/MPTeq/?page_id=229', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(230, 1, '2019-12-05 10:22:12', '2019-12-05 10:22:12', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MPTeq are proud to have a technology agreement with world mixing and agitation experts – Vmix Mineral Technologies, located in Bangalore, India and who have supplied over 4 000 mixers globally.&nbsp; MPTeq is the exclusive distributor to the complete VMix product range in Africa.&nbsp; All MPTeq products are manufactured in accordance with international standards and can be CE certified if required.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MPTeq has also partnered with the Metanza Group of Companies.&nbsp; Metanza Metallurgical Laboratories assists MPTeq with all test work requirements, while the full range of mineral processing jigs has been made available to the MPTeq product offering by Metanza Materials Handling.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Our Partners', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-partners', '', '', '2019-12-05 10:22:12', '2019-12-05 10:22:12', '', 0, 'https://cmfreelancing.co.za/client_sites/MPTeq/?page_id=230', 0, 'page', '', 0),
